---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Tagline from '../components/Tagline.astro';
---

<Layout title="Working With Us - Wellmade" description="No surprises. No black boxes. Here's exactly how we work.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">Working With Us</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80">
        No surprises. No black boxes.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 font-medium mt-4">
        We believe in transparency. Here's exactly how we work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- We Work in Days -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">We work in days.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Simple. Honest. Easy to track.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        No complex formulas. No hidden fees. No "consulting hours" that mean something different to everyone.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        A day is a day. You know what you're paying for.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three Ways to Engage -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-12">Three ways to engage.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Prepaid Bucket</h3>
          <p class="text-body mb-4">A block of days, used as needed. Flexible.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-body/70">Good for defined projects with clear scope.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Monthly Retainer</h3>
          <p class="text-body mb-4">A fixed number of days per month. Predictable.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-body/70">Good for ongoing collaboration.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Time & Materials</h3>
          <p class="text-body mb-4">Day by day, as the work requires.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-body/70">Good for discovery phases or uncertain scope.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why No Fixed Quotes -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Why no fixed quotes?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Building products isn't like ordering furniture.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Scope evolves. Discoveries happen. Priorities shift. A fixed quote either locks you into the wrong thing or hides a margin buffer for "surprises."
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        We'd rather stay flexible, communicate constantly, and never surprise you with the invoice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who Does the Work -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12">Who does the work.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent mb-3">Core team.</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80">Senior builders who are part of Wellmade. They lead, they ship, they stay.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent mb-3">Trusted network.</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80">Specialists we've worked with before. We know their work. We know they deliver. We know they won't vanish mid-project.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 font-medium mt-12">
        The people who start your project are the people who finish it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- When We Need External Expertise -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">When we need external expertise.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Sometimes a project needs a skill we don't have in-house or in our network.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
        When that happens, we don't disappear and come back with a name. We do it together:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-body">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold">1.</span>
          <span><strong class="text-title">We scope it with you.</strong> What do we actually need?</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold">2.</span>
          <span><strong class="text-title">We search together.</strong> We find candidates, you're in the loop.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold">3.</span>
          <span><strong class="text-title">We interview together.</strong> You meet them, you ask questions.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold">4.</span>
          <span><strong class="text-title">You choose, you contract.</strong> Direct relationship, no middleman markup.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold">5.</span>
          <span><strong class="text-title">We manage together.</strong> We integrate them into the project, we stay accountable.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium mt-8">
        Full transparency. No surprises. Your project, your team.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Communication -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Communication.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Communication is key. We don't disappear into a cave and emerge with code.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-title mb-2">Weekly sync.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Short, effective. What's done, what's next, what's blocked.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-title mb-2">Always available.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">During working hours on days we're booked with you, we're reachable. Slack, email, call - your choice.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-title mb-2">After hours?</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Our Support package covers critical issues when you need SLAs - especially for infrastructure. We'll talk about what that looks like for your situation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tools & Infrastructure -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Tools & Infrastructure.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Every project needs a stack: code repository, cloud, tools.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        For most, we use your existing setup or help you create your own accounts directly with providers. Your contracts, your control.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        Sometimes we need internal tools on our side. If there's a cost, you'll know before we start. No surprise line items.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Bus Factor -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">The Bus Factor.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        What happens if we get hit by a bus? What if you want to leave?
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We think about this from day one.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Your code lives on your infrastructure. Your accounts. Your repositories. You can pull the plug anytime - within contract terms, of course - and resume operations with any other provider.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        If you leave, we'll make sure you have everything. Documentation, context, access, answers to questions we forgot to write down.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 font-medium">
        We want you to leave happy. So you come back when you realize it was a mistake.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-6">Let's talk about your project.</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Tagline />
</Layout>
